                        <div class="head">
                            <h1>Prof. Dr. Alper Uçak</h1>
                            <h2>Kalp ve Damar Cerrahisi</h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tab-content-sec">
                            <ul class="nav nav-tabs" id="myTab" role="tablist">
                                <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
                                    <button class="nav-link active" id="speciality-tab" data-bs-toggle="tab" data-bs-target="#speciality-tab-pane" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="speciality-tab-pane" aria-selected="true">Uzmanlıklar</button>
                                </li>
                                <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
                                    <button class="nav-link" id="education-tab" data-bs-toggle="tab" data-bs-target="#education-tab-pane" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="education-tab-pane" aria-selected="false">Eğitim</button>
                                </li>
                                <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
                                    <button class="nav-link" id="publications-tab" data-bs-toggle="tab" data-bs-target="#publications-tab-pane" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="publications-tab-pane" aria-selected="false">Yayınlar/Deneyim</button>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                            <div class="tab-content" id="myTabContent">
                                <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="speciality-tab-pane" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="speciality-tab" tabindex="0">
                                    <p>Tıbbi İlgi Alanları: A&ccedil;ık Kalp Ameliyatları, Kapalı Kalp Ameliyatları, Karotis Arter ve Periferik Arter Hastalığı, Endovask&uuml;ler Tedavi Y&ouml;ntemleri (Aort Anevrizması, Derin Ven Trombozu, Periferik Arter Hastalığında), Varis Hastalığında Modern Tedavi Y&ouml;ntemleri (Endoven&ouml;z Radyofrekans Ablasyon, Laser Ablasyon, Yapıştırma Tekniği), K&ouml;p&uuml;k Tedavisi</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="tab-pane fade" id="education-tab-pane" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="education-tab" tabindex="0">
                                    <p>GATA Tıp Fak&uuml;ltesi / 1998</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="tab-pane fade" id="publications-tab-pane" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="publications-tab" tabindex="0">
                                    <p>1. &nbsp; &nbsp;Thoracic endoscopic surgery for hyperhidrosis: comparison of different techniques<br>BİLAL KAAN İNAN, ONUR SEL&Ccedil;UK G&Ouml;KSEL, ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, VEYSEL TEMİZKAN, MEHMET KEREM KARACA, MURAT UĞUR, G&Ouml;KHAN ARSLAN, MELİH HULUSİ us,AHMET TURAN YILMAZ , Yayın Yeri: Thoracic endoscopic surgery for hyperhidrosis: comparison of different techniques , 2022<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded &Ouml;zg&uuml;n Makale</p>
<p>2. &nbsp; &nbsp;0022-4804.<br>SUZAN SA&Ccedil;AR, MUSTAFA SA&Ccedil;AR, H AYBEK, H TURGUT, G&Ouml;KHAN &Ouml;NEM, N CEVAHİR, Z TEKE, I KALELİ, ADEM G&Uuml;LER, ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, AHMET BALTALARLI, Yayın Yeri: Comparison of the therapeutic efficacy of linezolid and vancomycin and correlation of serum and tissue malondialdehyde and myeloperoxidase in an experimental mediastinitis model, 2022<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded &Ouml;zg&uuml;n Makale</p>
<p>3. &nbsp; &nbsp;A retrospective comparison of bovine pericardium and polytetrafluoroethylene patch for closure of ventricular septal defects.<br>ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, Yayın Yeri: The J of Int Med Res, 2022<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded &Ouml;zg&uuml;n Makale</p>
<p>4. &nbsp; &nbsp; Comparison of 3 different incisions used for atrial-septal defect closure<br>MURAT BAŞARAN, ALİ KOCAİLİK, İSMAİL CİHAN &Ouml;ZBEK, ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, EYL&Uuml;L KAFALI, MELİH HULUSİ us, Yayın Yeri: Heart Surg Forum, 2022<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded &Ouml;zg&uuml;n Makale</p>
<p>5. &nbsp; &nbsp;Is saphenofemoral junction reconstruction necessary during stripping of the saphanous vein?<br>MELİH HULUSİ us,İSMAİL CİHAN &Ouml;ZBEK,MURAT BAŞARAN,ALPER U&Ccedil;AK,SONER SANİOĞLU,Y&Uuml;CESİN ARSLAN,NOYAN TEMU&Ccedil;İN OĞUŞ,AHMET TURAN YILMAZ , Yayın Yeri: surgery , 2022<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded &Ouml;zg&uuml;n Makale</p>
<p>6. &nbsp; &nbsp; Surgical removal of a pacemaker lead causing infective endocarditis: A case report<br>MUSTAFA SA&Ccedil;AR, T&Uuml;NAY KURTOĞLU,harun d&uuml;ver,BİLAL KAAN İNAN,ADEM G&Uuml;LER,ALPER U&Ccedil;AK,MELİH HULUSİ us,AHMET TURAN YILMAZ , Yayın Yeri: Trends Biomater Artif Organs , 2022<br>Uluslararası Hakemli AHCI Vaka Takdimi</p>
<p>7. &nbsp; &nbsp;Inferior mesenteric artery aneurysm combined with renal artery stenosis in a patient with neurofibromatosis<br>MUSTAFA SA&Ccedil;AR, ENGİN TULUKOĞLU, ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, ADEM G&Uuml;LER, AHMET TURAN YILMAZ, Yayın Yeri: Inferior mesenteric artery aneurysm combined with renal artery stenosis in a patient with neurofibromatosis. , 2022<br>Uluslararası Hakemli AHCI Vaka Takdimi</p>
<p>8. &nbsp; &nbsp;Videoendoscopic retroperitoneal lumbar sympathectomy for selected cases: A new technique<br>BİLAL KAAN İNAN, ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, MUSTAFA SA&Ccedil;AR, ADEM G&Uuml;LER, MELİH HULUSİ us,AHMET TURAN YILMAZ , Yayın Yeri: The nigerian journal of surgical research , 2022<br>Uluslararası Hakemli Endekste taranmıyor &Ouml;zg&uuml;n Makale</p>
<p>9. &nbsp; &nbsp;The Effect of Serum Intestinal and Peritoneal Visfatin Levels on Early Diagnosis of Acute Mesenteric Ischemia<br>ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, VEYSEL TEMİZKAN, H&Uuml;SEYİN ŞEN, BULUT ERMAN CANER, MURAT FATİH CAN, MURAT UĞUR, SEL&Ccedil;UK ARİF, ZAFER K&Uuml;&Ccedil;&Uuml;KODACI, &Ouml;MER &Ouml;ZCAN, Yayın Yeri: INTERNATIONAL ANGIOLOGY, 2015<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded &Ouml;zg&uuml;n Makale</p>
<p>10. &nbsp; &nbsp;Removal of broken catheter piece with snare device during endovascular treatment of post traumatic brachial artery pseudo aneurysm case report<br>VEYSEL TEMİZKAN, ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, İBRAHİM ALP, CAN MURAT FATİH, G&Ouml;KHAN ARSLAN, YILMAZ AHMET TURAN, Yayın Yeri: Cardiovascular Journal Of Africa, 2015<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded Vaka Takdimi &nbsp;&nbsp;<br>https://dx.doi.org/10.5830/CVJA-2015-025&nbsp;</p>
<p>11. &nbsp; &nbsp;Ruptured mitral valve aneurysm due to infective endocarditis<br>ZAFER IŞILAK, UĞUR K&Uuml;&Ccedil;&Uuml;K, ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, &Ouml;MER UZ, MEHMET DOĞAN, Yayın Yeri: European Heart Journal - Cardiovascular Imaging, 2015<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded Vaka Takdimi &nbsp;&nbsp;<br>https://dx.doi.org/10.1093/ehjci/jeu310&nbsp;</p>
<p>12. &nbsp; &nbsp;Four different strategies for repair of aortic coarctation accompanied by cardiac lesions<br>MURAT UĞUR, İBRAHİM ALP, G&Ouml;KHAN ARSLAN, VEYSEL TEMİZKAN, ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, AHMET TURAN YILMAZ, Yayın Yeri: INTERACTIVE CARDIOVASCULAR AND THORACIC SURGERY, 2013<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded &Ouml;zg&uuml;n Makale &nbsp;&nbsp;<br>https://dx.doi.org/10.1093/icvts/ivt242&nbsp;</p>
<p>13. &nbsp; &nbsp;Endovascular and hybrid treatment in the management of vascular disease experience of a cardiovascular surgery department<br>MURAT UĞUR, İBRAHİM ALP, G&Ouml;KHAN ARSLAN, ŞAHİN ŞENAY, İSMAİL SEL&Ccedil;UK, ARİF SEL&Ccedil;UK, VEYSEL TEMİZKAN, ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, AHMET TURAN YILMAZ, Yayın Yeri: T&Uuml;RK G&Ouml;G&Uuml;S KALP DAMAR CERRAHİSİ DERGİSİ, 2012<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded &Ouml;zg&uuml;n Makale &nbsp; https://dx.doi.org/10.5606/tgkdc.dergisi.2012.046&nbsp;</p>
<p>14. &nbsp; &nbsp;Minimally Invasive Hybrid Treatment of Acute Type I Aortic Dissection A Single Stage Technique without Circulatory Arrest<br>AHMET TURAN YILMAZ, ŞAHİN ŞENAY, ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, Yayın Yeri: TEXAS HEART INSTITUTE JOURNAL, 2012<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded Vaka Takdimi</p>
<p>15. &nbsp; &nbsp;Rosuvastatin a New Generation 3 Hydroxy 3 Methylglutaryl Coenzyme A Reductase Inhibitor Reduces Ischemia Reperfusion Induced Spinal Cord Tissue Injury in Rats<br>ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, BURAK ONAN, ADEM G&Uuml;LER, MEHMET ALİ ŞAHİN, OĞUZ KILI&Ccedil;KAYA, EMİN &Ouml;ZTAŞ, B&Uuml;LENT UYSAL, SIDDIK ARSLAN, AHMET TURAN YILMAZ, Yayın Yeri: ANNALS OF VASCULAR SURGERY, 2011<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded &Ouml;zg&uuml;n Makale &nbsp; https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.avsg.2011.02.024&nbsp;</p>
<p>16. &nbsp; &nbsp;The Effects of Gabapentin on Acute and Chronic Postoperative Pain After Coronary Artery Bypass Graft Surgery<br>ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, ONAN BURAK, H&Uuml;SEYİN ŞEN, İSMAİL SEL&Ccedil;UK, ALPASLAN TURAN, YILMAZ AHMET TURAN, Yayın Yeri: JOURNAL OF CARDIOTHORACIC AND VASCULAR ANESTHESIA, 2011<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded &Ouml;zg&uuml;n Makale &nbsp; https://dx.doi.org/10.1053/j.jvca.2010.11.017&nbsp;</p>
<p>17. &nbsp; &nbsp;Protective Effects of Angiotensin II Type 1 Receptor Blockade With Olmesartan on Spinal Cord Ischemia Reperfusion Injury An Experimental Study on Rats<br>ADEM G&Uuml;LER, MEHMET ALİ ŞAHİN, ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, BURAK ONAN, BİLAL KAAN İNAN, EMİN &Ouml;ZTAŞ, SIDDIK ARSLAN, B&Uuml;LENT UYSAL, UFUK DEMİRKILI&Ccedil;, HARUN TATAR, Yayın Yeri: ANNALS OF VASCULAR SURGERY, 2010<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded &Ouml;zg&uuml;n Makale &nbsp; https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.avsg.2010.03.023&nbsp;</p>
<p>18. &nbsp; &nbsp;Endocardial Fibroelastosis of the Right Ventricle and Tricuspid Valve in a Young Adult with Behcet s Disease<br>ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, BURAK ONAN, BİLAL KAAN İNAN, MURAT UĞUR, ZAFER K&Uuml;&Ccedil;&Uuml;KODACI, AHMET TURAN YILMAZ, Yayın Yeri: JOURNAL OF CARDIAC SURGERY, 2010<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded Vaka Takdimi &nbsp;&nbsp;<br>https://dx.doi.org/10.1111/j.1540-8191.2010.01004.x&nbsp;</p>
<p>19. &nbsp; &nbsp;Hemorrhage Into a Pericardial Cyst and Associated Right Ventricular Compression After Blunt Chest Trauma<br>VEYSEL TEMİZKAN, BURAK ONAN, BİLAL KAAN İNAN, ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, AHMET TURAN YILMAZ, Yayın Yeri: ANNALS OF THORACIC SURGERY, 2010<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded Vaka Takdimi &nbsp; https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.athoracsur.2009.09.018&nbsp;</p>
<p>20. &nbsp; &nbsp;Protective Effects of Angiotensin II Type 1 Receptor Blockade With Olmesartan on Spinal Cord Ischemia Reperfusion Injury An Experimental Study on Rats<br>Adem G&uuml;ler, Mehmet Ali Şahin, ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, Burak Onan, Kaan İnan, EMİN &Ouml;ZTAŞ, Sıddık Arslan,B&Uuml;LENT UYSAL, UFUK DEMİRKILI&Ccedil;, Harun Tatar, Yayın Yeri: Annals of Vascular Surgery, 2010<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded &Ouml;zg&uuml;n Makale &nbsp; https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.avsg.2010.03.023&nbsp;</p>
<p>21. &nbsp; &nbsp;Free Floating Tumor Thrombus in the Left Atrium Associated with Non Small Cell Lung Cancer<br>ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, BİLAL KAAN İNAN, BURAK ONAN, VEYSEL TEMİZKAN, İBRAHİM ALP, AHMET TURAN YILMAZ, Yayın Yeri: Journal of Cardiac Surgery, 2009<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded Vaka Takdimi &nbsp;&nbsp;<br>https://dx.doi.org/10.1111/j.1540-8191.2009.00927.x&nbsp;</p>
<p>22. &nbsp; &nbsp;Comparison of the Therapeutic Efficacy of Linezolid and Vancomycin and Correlation of Serum and Tissue Malondialdehyde and Myeloperoxidase in an Experimental Mediastinitis Model<br>SUZAN SA&Ccedil;AR, MUSTAFA SA&Ccedil;AR, H&Uuml;LYA AYBEK, H&Uuml;SEYİN TURGUT, G&Ouml;KHAN &Ouml;NEM, ZAFER TEKE, NURAL CEVAHİR, İLKNUR KALELİ, ADEM G&Uuml;LER, ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, AHMET BALTALARLI, Yayın Yeri: JOURNAL OF SURGICAL RESEARCH, 2009<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded &Ouml;zg&uuml;n Makale &nbsp; https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.jss.2008.03.040&nbsp;</p>
<p>23. &nbsp; &nbsp;Left Main Coronary Artery and Supravalvular Aortic Stenosis in Adult Treatment with Ostial Patchplasty and Modified Brom Procedure<br>BİLAL KAAN İNAN, ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, AHMET &Uuml;MİT G&Uuml;LL&Uuml;, VEYSEL TEMİZKAN, MURAT UĞUR, AHMET TURAN YILMAZ, Yayın Yeri: JOURNAL OF CARDIAC SURGERY, 2009<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded &Ouml;zg&uuml;n Makale &nbsp;&nbsp;<br>https://dx.doi.org/10.1111/j.1540-8191.2008.00795.x&nbsp;</p>
<p>24. &nbsp; &nbsp;Pulmonary Vascular Protective Mechanisms in Adult Patients with an Isolated Large Ventricular Septal Defect A 21 Year Experience<br>BİLAL KAAN İNAN, ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, VEYSEL TEMİZKAN, KORAY AK, H&Uuml;SEYİN ŞEN, AHMET TURAN YILMAZ, Yayın Yeri: JOURNAL OF CARDIAC SURGERY, 2009<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded &Ouml;zg&uuml;n Makale &nbsp;&nbsp;<br>https://dx.doi.org/10.1111/j.1540-8191.2009.00913.x&nbsp;</p>
<p>25. &nbsp; &nbsp;Thoracic endoscopic surgery for hyperhidrosis Comparison of different techniques<br>BİLAL KAAN İNAN, ONUR SEL&Ccedil;UK G&Ouml;KSEL, ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, VEYSEL TEMİZKAN, MEHMET KEREM KARACA, MURAT UĞUR, G&Ouml;KHAN ARSLAN, MELİH HULUSİ US, AHMET TURAN YILMAZ, Yayın Yeri: THORACIC AND CARDIOVASCULAR SURGEON, 2008<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded &Ouml;zg&uuml;n Makale &nbsp;&nbsp;<br>https://dx.doi.org/10.1055/s-2007-989327&nbsp;</p>
<p>26. &nbsp; &nbsp;Erdosteine ameliorates lung injury induced by transient aortic occlusion in rats<br>T&Uuml;NAY KURTOĞLU, MUSTAFA SA&Ccedil;AR, BİLAL KAAN İNAN, harun d&uuml;ver, ADEM G&Uuml;LER, ALPER U&Ccedil;AK, MELİH HULUSİ us, AHMET TURAN YILMAZ, Yayın Yeri: Cardiovasc J of Africa, 2007<br>Uluslararası Hakemli SCI-Expanded &Ouml;zg&uuml;n Makale</p>
